Additionally, you can customize your drone's flight, using the following sliders:
*Motor Power: 2.0-12.0
*Drone Drag: 0.50-1.50
*Drone Cross Section Area: 0.010-0.050
*Drone Mass: 0.10-0.25
*Camera Tilt: 0.0-70.0
*Pitch Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Roll Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Yaw Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Throttle Rate: 0.25-1.00
*Pitch Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Roll Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Yaw Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Throttle Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Pitch Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Roll Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Yaw Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Throttle Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Self-Leveling Max Angle: 10.0-45.0
*Mode Change Smoothing: 0.0-1.00